The latest version of this appender is located at https://github.com/yoneal/log4net-4-scribe.

Introduction
============

Scribe is a server for aggregating log data that's streamed in real
time from clients. It is designed to be scalable and reliable. For more information regarding Scribe, please see https://github.com/facebook/scribe.

Apache log4net is a sub project of the Apache Logging Services project. 
It is a logging library similar for .NET.
Web site: http://logging.apache.org/log4net

Scribe Appender is a custom appender for log4net. It sends logging events to a running Scribe server.

Example
=======

For an example usage of this appender, please see the example folder.

